Pre-Game Insights: Hong Kong, China are set to face Iran in a highly anticipated match at the AFC Asian Cup 2023.
Iran will look to secure their place in the knockouts with a win, while Hong Kong, China aim to bounce back from a poor form.
Mehdi Taremi and Everton Camargo are key players to watch for Iran and Hong Kong, China respectively.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match will be telecasted in various countries, including India, Qatar, and others.
Iran is missing Ali Gholizadeh due to injury.
